or you.\nTell me. I like you.\nWe are laying factory. They are very company.\nWe are a bigger factory. Come on,\ncome on. Take a link.\nWhy don\'t you?\nWhy don\'t you take them? They are very company.\nCome on, come on,\ntake them. Dinner is being waiting.', '2026-03-30 03:19:00', '2026-03-30 03:19:10', 'AI 分析失败：The service encountered an unexpected internal error. Please retry later. Request id: 0217748407492557825215af71fb70e72d1e47bc500fa86ffaec8 {\"error\":{\"code\":\"InternalServiceError\",\"message\":\"The service encountered an unexpected internal error. Please retry later. Request id: 0217748407492557825215af71fb70e72d1e47bc500fa86ffaec8\",\"param\":\"\",\"type\":\"Internal Server Error\"}} 500 {\'error\': {\'code\': \'InternalServiceError\', \'message\': \'The service encountered an unexpected internal error. Please retry later. Request id: 0217748407492557825215af71fb70e72d1e47bc500fa86ffaec8\', \'param\': \'\', \'type\': \'Internal Server Error\'}} {\'server\': \'istio-envoy\', \'date\': \'Mon, 30 Mar 2026 03:19:09 GMT\', \'content-type\': \'application/json; charset=utf-8\', \'content-encoding\': \'gzip\', \'content-length\': \'197\', \'vary\': \'Accept-Encoding\', \'x-envoy-upstream-service-time\': \'188\', \'x-request-id\': \'0217748407492557825215af71fb70e72d1e47bc500fa86ffaec8\'}', '/uploads/downloads/5ab56960b04a430f8c38bb91a9e7b6da.mp4', 'idle', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'analysis', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `os_video_project` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `source_url`, `source_platform`, `status`, `objective`, `summary`, `full_text`, `dialogue_text`, `narration_text`, `caption_text`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `ai_analysis`, `media_url`, `remake_generation_status`, `remake_generation_provider`, `remake_generation_model`, `remake_generation_objective`, `remake_generation_asset_type`, `remake_generation_asset_name`, `remake_generation_asset_url`, `remake_generation_reference_frames`, `remake_generation_script`, `remake_generation_storyboard`, `remake_generation_prompt`, `remake_generation_task_id`, `remake_generation_result_url`, `remake_generation_error`, `remake_generation_updated_at`, `workflow_type`, `analysis_reference_frames`, `analysis_visual_features`, `remake_generation_audio_name`, `remake_generation_audio_url`) VALUES (7, 1, '分析脚本 · https://www.tiktok.com/@auto.parts.store.tina/video/7619658308009528596', 'https://www.tiktok.com/@auto.parts.store.tina/video/7619658308009528596', 'tiktok', 'ready', '从这个视频中提取完整的文本脚本，包括对话、旁白以及所有文字字幕：', '已基于真实视频解析完成 TikTok 来源 7619658308009528596 的拆解，通过 subtitles 提取了 11 段文本。 视频时长约 27.9 秒。', '[caption] Hello, boss.\n[caption] How are you? I\'m Tina.\n[caption] Do you know I will be waiting for you.\n[caption] Tell me. I like you.\n[caption] We are laying factory. They are very company.\n[caption] We are a bigger factory. Come on,\n[caption] come on. Take a link.\n[caption] Why don\'t you?\n[caption] Why don\'t you take them? They are very company.\n[caption] Come on, come on,\n[caption] take them. Dinner is being waiting.', 'Hello, boss.\nHow are you? I\'m Tina.\nDo you know I will be waiting for you.\nTell me. I like you.\nWe are laying factory. They are very company.\nWe are a bigger factory. Come on,\ncome on. Take a link.\nWhy don\'t you?\nWhy don\'t you take them? They are very company.\nCome on, come on,\ntake them. Dinner is being waiting.', '', 'Hello, boss.\nHow are you? I\'m Tina.\nDo you know I will be waiting for you.\nTell me. I like you.\nWe are laying factory. They are very company.\nWe are a bigger factory. Come on,\ncome on. Take a link.\nWhy don\'t you?\nWhy don\'t you take them? They are very company.\nCome on, come on,\ntake them. Dinner is being waiting.', '2026-03-30 03:46:39', '2026-03-30 03:47:50', '## 一、视频脚本整理（Script Extraction）\n[00:03 - 00:03]: Hello, boss.  \n[00:03 - 00:05]: How are you? I\'m Tina.  \n[00:05 - 00:08]: Do you know I\'ve been waiting for you?  \n[00:08 - 00:10]: Tell me, I like you.  \n[00:10 - 00:13]: We are a manufacturing factory. We are a reliable company.  \n[00:13 - 00:15]: We are a big factory. Come on,  \n[00:15 - 00:17]: come on. Take the link.  \n[00:17 - 00:18]: Why don\'t you?  \n[00:19 - 00:22]: Why don\'t you take it? We are a reliable company.  \n[00:22 - 00:23]: Come on, come on,  \n[00:23 - 00:25]: take it. Dinner is waiting.  \n\n\n## 二、视频结构拆解（Structure Breakdown）\n\n### 1. Hook（0-3秒）  \n- 内容：[00:03] \"Hello, boss.\"  \n- 类型：人设型（试图通过称呼建立亲切感）  \n- 吸引点：使用\"boss\"称呼拉近与观众距离  \n- 是否有效（强/中/弱）：弱  \n- 原因分析：仅单一问候语，无产品/痛点/利益点关联，无法快速抓住用户注意力；3秒内未传递任何核心价值，用户易划走。  \n\n### 2. Product Demo（产品展示）  \n- 展示方式：无（全程无产品画面/功能/场景展示）  \n- 信息传递效率：低  \n- 是否建立信任：否  \n- 存在问题：未展示任何产品实物、生产流程或使用场景，用户无法感知\"工厂\"对应的产品类型及价值，信任基础缺失。  \n\n### 3. Value Proposition（核心卖点）  \n- 核心卖点提炼：  \n  1. \"We are a big factory\"（工厂规模大）  \n  2. \"We are a reliable company\"（公司可靠）  \n- 是否重复强化：是（\"reliable company\"重复2次）  \n- 是否击中用户痛点：否（未提及用户需求，如\"找源头工厂\"\"降低成本\"\"保证质量\"等）  \n- 缺失点：未明确产品类型（如服装/电子/家居）、核心优势（如价格/产能/定制能力）、差异化价值（如专利技术/快速交付）。  \n\n### 4. Call-To-Action（转化引导）  \n- CTA内容：\"Take the link\" \"Why don\'t you take it?\" \"come on, take it\"  \n- 类型：强引导（直接要求点击链接）  \n- 紧迫感：弱（仅用\"Dinner is waiting\"暗示时间有限，但逻辑牵强）  \n- 转化效率评估：低（未说明链接内容<如报价单/产品目录>、点击价值<如\"领工厂底价\">，用户无明确行动动机）  \n\n\n## 三、用户心理分析（Consumer Psychology）  \n- 信任建立：试图通过\"big factory\"\"reliable company\"建立信任，但无具体证据（如工厂实拍/客户案例/资质证书），信任度极低。  \n- 稀缺感：无（未提及限量/限时/独家资源，无法触发\"怕错过\"心理）。  \n- 从众/权威感：无（无客户评价/行业认证/销量数据，无法体现\"大家都在合作\"或\"专业可靠\"）。  \n- 情绪驱动：无明确情绪导向（\"Dinner is waiting\"试图制造轻微紧迫感，但与商业转化无关；\"I like you\"试图拉近距离，但过度个人化，与B2B/B2C带货场景脱节）。  \n\n\n## 四、电商转化评分（E-commerce Score）  \n- 吸引力（Hook）：2/10（仅靠\"boss\"称呼微弱拉近距离，无实质内容）  \n- 产品表达：0/10（全程无产品信息，用户不知\"买什么\"）  \n- 信任构建：1/10（空泛强调\"可靠\"，无实证支撑）  \n- 转化引导：2/10（强引导但无行动理由，用户无点击动力）  \n- 综合评分：1.25/10  \n\n**总结评价**：视频缺乏核心要素（产品展示、明确卖点、信任证据），转化链路断裂，无法实现商业目标。  \n\n\n## 五、优化建议（Actionable Suggestions）  \n1. **Hook优化**（替换文案）：  \n   \"Boss, need a reliable factory for [产品类型，如\"3C accessories\"]? 500+ clients trust us—click to check our price list!\"（直接点明用户身份+产品+核心价值，3秒内抓住B端采购痛点）  \n\n2. **视频内容优化**（镜头/结构建议）：  \n   - 0-3秒：工厂大门/生产线全景镜头+Hook文案；  \n   - 3-10秒：特写产品细节（如材质/功能）+生产流程（如质检环节）；  \n   - 10-15秒：客户合作案例（如\"Supplied 100k units to Walmart\"）+资质证书（ISO/BSCI认证）；  \n   - 15-20秒：核心卖点（\"Factory price 30% lower than traders\"\"7-day delivery\"）。  \n\n3. **卖点强化建议**：  \n   - 明确产品品类（如\"we are a big factory for wireless chargers\"）；  \n   - 量化优势（\"10,000㎡ factory, 5 production lines, 500k monthly capacity\"）；  \n   - 解决用户痛点（\"No middleman—save 30% cost\"\"Custom logo accepted\"）。  \n\n4. **CTA优化**（新话术）：  \n   \"Click the link below to get your FREE sample + factory price list! Only 20 slots left today—act fast!\"（明确链接价值+稀缺性，降低行动门槛）  \n\n5. **是否建议投流**：否  \n   原因：当前视频缺乏产品、卖点、信任等核心转化要素，投流会导致高曝光低转化，浪费预算；需先优化内容基础。  \n\n\n## 六、爆款潜力判断（Viral Potential）  \n- 是否具备爆款潜力：低  \n- 原因：内容混乱（无产品焦点）、卖点模糊（未解决用户需求）、信任缺失（无实证支撑），无法引发用户共鸣或分享欲。  \n- 适合投放市场：无（当前内容无法匹配任何市场需求；若优化后聚焦\"高性价比工厂货源\"，可尝试东南亚B2B市场<如印尼/越南>，该区域对源头工厂需求较高）。', '/uploads/downloads/049ff2aabee44ccb8761fb3397e55b65.mp4', 'idle', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'analysis', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `os_video_project` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `source_url`, `source_platform`, `status`, `objective`, `summary`, `full_text`, `dialogue_text`, `narration_text`, `caption_text`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `ai_analysis`, `media_url`, `remake_generation_status`, `remake_generation_provider`, `remake_generation_model`, `remake_generation_objective`, `remake_generation_asset_type`, `remake_generation_asset_name`, `remake_generation_asset_url`, `remake_generation_reference_frames`, `remake_generation_script`, `remake_generation_storyboard`, `remake_generation_prompt`, `remake_generation_task_id`, `remake_generation_result_url`, `remake_generation_error`, `remake_generation_updated_at`, `workflow_type`, `analysis_reference_frames`, `analysis_visual_features`, `remake_generation_audio_name`, `remake_generation_audio_url`) VALUES (8, 1, '复刻爆款 · https://www.tiktok.com/@auto.parts.store.tina/video/7619658308009528596', 'https://www.tiktok.com/@auto.parts.store.tina/video/7619658308009528596', 'tiktok', 'ready', '复刻这个视频的画面细节，包括画面构图、色彩、光影等：', 'Your account [2102011634] has reached the set inference limit for the [doubao-seedance-1-5-pro] model, and the model service has been paused. To continue using this model, please visit the Model Activation page to adjust or close the \"Safe Experience Mode\". Request id: 02177485715509900000000000000000000ffffac177d51d48e79', '[caption] Hello, boss.\n[caption] How are you? I\'m Tina.\n[caption] Do you know I will be waiting for you.\n[caption] Tell me. I like you.\n[caption] We are laying factory. They are very company.\n[caption] We are a bigger factory. Come on,\n[caption] come on. Take a link.\n[caption] Why don\'t you?\n[caption] Why don\'t you take them? They are very company.\n[caption] Come on, come on,\n[caption] take them. Dinner is being waiting.', 'Hello, boss.\nHow are you? I\'m Tina.\nDo you know I will be waiting for you.\nTell me. I like you.\nWe are laying factory. They are very company.\nWe are a bigger factory. Come on,\ncome on. Take a link.\nWhy don\'t you?\nWhy don\'t you take them? They are very company.\nCome on, come on,\ntake them. Dinner is being waiting.', '', 'Hello, boss.\nHow are you? I\'m Tina.\nDo you know I will be waiting for you.\nTell me. I like you.\nWe are laying factory. They are very company.\nWe are a bigger factory. Come on,\ncome on. Take a link.\nWhy don\'t you?\nWhy don\'t you take them? They are very company.\nCome on, come on,\ntake them. Dinner is being waiting.', '2026-03-30 07:17:34', '2026-03-30 07:52:41', 'TikTok 电商效果深度分析  \n核心营销打法：通过“老板”亲切称呼拉近B端客户距离，以工厂身份直接引导点击链接，但缺乏产品展示和清晰卖点。\n\n\n1. Hook（钩子）  \n时间：00:03 - 00:05  \n内容：“Hello, boss. How are you? I\'m Tina.”  \n分析：  \n- 策略：使用“boss”（老板）直接称呼目标用户（B端采购商），结合自我介绍快速建立亲近感，试图降低陌生感。  \n- 效果：针对性称呼可能吸引B端决策者注意力，但缺乏视觉钩子（如工厂场景、产品特写），单纯口播吸引力有限。  \n\n\n2. Product Demo（产品展示）  \n时间：当前素材未体现  \n内容：当前素材未体现  \n分析：  \n- 策略：当前素材未体现  \n- 效果：当前素材未体现  \n\n\n3. Value Proposition（价值主张）  \n时间：00:10 - 00:15  \n内容：“We are laying factory. They are very company. We are a bigger factory.”  \n分析：  \n- 策略：试图强调“工厂身份”和“规模优势”（bigger factory），传递供应链实力。  \n- 效果：信息模糊且存在语法错误（“laying factory”“very company”语义不明），无法让用户理解工厂核心优势（如产能、资质、产品类型等），价值主张不清晰。  \n\n\n4. Call-to-Action（行动呼吁）  \n时间：00:15 - 00:25  \n内容：“come on, take a link. Why don\'t you take them? They are very company. Come on, come on, take them. Dinner is being waiting.”  \n分析：  \n- 策略：高频重复“come on”“take a link”“take them”，试图通过催促式语言推动用户点击链接。  \n- 效果：CTA文案模糊（“take them”未明确指代产品/链接），且“Dinner is being waiting”与营销目标无关，无法激发用户行动动机，转化引导无效。  \n\n\n5. 字幕整理  \n- 00:03 - 00:03 | Hello, boss.  \n- 00:03 - 00:05 | How are you? I\'m Tina.  \n- 00:05 - 00:08 | Do you know I will be waiting for you.  \n- 00:08 - 00:10 | Tell me. I like you.  \n- 00:10 - 00:13 | We are laying factory. They are very company.  \n- 00:13 - 00:15 | We are a bigger factory. Come on,  \n- 00:15 - 00:17 | come on. Take a link.  \n- 00:17 - 00:18 | Why don\'t you?  \n- 00:19 - 00:22 | Why don\'t you take them? They are very company.  \n- 00:22 - 00:23 | Come on, come on,  \n- 00:23 - 00:25 | take them. Dinner is being waiting.  \n\n\n6. 转化评分  \n- 信任建立：0/10（无工厂实拍、资质证明、客户案例等信任背书）  \n- 产品展示：0/10（未提及任何产品信息或展示）  \n- 卖点清晰：2/10（仅模糊提到“bigger factory”，无具体优势说明）  \n- 行动引导：3/10（有CTA但文案模糊，无法明确行动目标）  \n- 综合评分：1/10  \n- 总评：缺乏产品核心信息、信任背书和清晰卖点，转化能力极弱。  \n\n\n7. 爆款潜力  \n- 结论：低  \n- 原因：无产品展示、价值主张模糊、信任缺失，无法满足B端用户“看产品、验工厂、明优势”的核心需求。  \n- 适合市场/人群：理论适合B2B采购商，但当前内容无法吸引目标用户。  \n\n\n8. 专家建议  \n1. **字幕优化**：修正语法错误，明确核心信息。例如将“We are laying factory. They are very company.”改为“我们是实力工厂，10年专注XX产品生产（如纺织/电子）”；“Dinner is being waiting”删除，避免无关信息干扰。  \n2. **产品细节展示**：添加3-5秒产品特写镜头（如产品外观、功能测试、应用场景），配合字幕“主营XX产品（如户外帐篷/无线耳机），支持定制/批量采购”。  \n3. **卖点强化**：用具体数据替代模糊描述，例如“10000㎡工厂，日产能5000件，通过ISO9001认证”，增强工厂实力可信度。  \n4. **CTA文案优化**：将“take a link”改为明确行动指令，如“点击链接获取工厂报价单”“私信我发产品目录”，并在视频角落添加“立即咨询”按钮贴纸。  \n5. **私信转化动作**：口播补充“私信回复‘样品’免费领取测试样”，引导用户主动私信，提升询盘转化。', '/uploads/downloads/0cab5388fa174f798a17fdc644fce515.mp4', 'failed', NULL, NULL, '复刻这个视频的画面细节，包括画面构图、色彩、光影等：', 'image', '20260325180045_586_43.png', 'upload://reference-assets/2026/03/30/4d0afb481be341fc96ed829502218b8b-20260325180045_586_43.png', '[\"/uploads/reference-assets/2026/03/30/4d0afb481be341fc96ed829502218b8b-20260325180045_586_43.png\"]', '镜头 1：Hello, boss. How are you? I\'m Tina. Do you know I will be waiting for you.\n镜头 2：Tell me. I like you. We are laying factory. They are very company. We are a bigger factory. Come on,\n镜头 3：come on. Take a link. Why don\'t you? Why don\'t you take them? They are very company.\n镜头 4：Come on, come on, take them. Dinner is being waiting.', '镜头 1：画面 竖屏镜头，参考 3.1s - 8.3s 的原视频节奏。 当前任务目标：复刻这个视频的画面细节，包括画面构图、色彩、光影等：。；拍摄提示 围绕这段真实内容复刻画面与镜头推进：Hello, boss. How are you? I\'m Tina. Do you know I will be waiting for you.；旁白 Hello, boss. How are you? I\'m Tina. Do you know I will be waiting for you.；字幕 Hello, boss.；剪辑 保持 TikTok 的剪辑速度，参考 32.31fps 与 1080x1920，整条视频时长约 27.9 秒。。\n镜头 2：画面 竖屏镜头，参考 8.3s - 15.8s 的原视频节奏。 当前任务目标：复刻这个视频的画面细节，包括画面构图、色彩、光影等：。；拍摄提示 围绕这段真实内容复刻画面与镜头推进：Tell me. I like you. We are laying factory. They are very company. We are a bigger factory. Come on,；旁白 Tell me. I like you. We are laying factory. They are very company. We are a bigger factory. Come on,；字幕 Tell me. I like you.；剪辑 保持 TikTok 的剪辑速度，参考 32.31fps 与 1080x1920，整条视频时长约 27.9 秒。。\n镜头 3：画面 竖屏镜头，参考 15.8s - 22.3s 的原视频节奏。 当前任务目标：复刻这个视频的画面细节，包括画面构图、色彩、光影等：。；拍摄提示 围绕这段真实内容复刻画面与镜头推进：come on. Take a link. Why don\'t you? Why don\'t you take them? They are very company.；旁白 come on. Take a link. Why don\'t you? Why don\'t you take them? They are very company.；字幕 come on. Take a link.；剪辑 保持 TikTok 的剪辑速度，参考 32.31fps 与 1080x1920，整条视频时长约 27.9 秒。。\n镜头 4：画面 竖屏镜头，参考 22.4s - 25.9s 的原视频节奏。 当前任务目标：复刻这个视频的画面细节，包括画面构图、色彩、光影等：。；拍摄提示 围绕这段真实内容复刻画面与镜头推进：Come on, come on, take them. Dinner is being waiting.；旁白 Come on, come on, take them. Dinner is being waiting.；字幕 Come on, come on,；剪辑 保持 TikTok 的剪辑速度，参考 32.31fps 与 1080x1920，整条视频时长约 27.9 秒。。', 'Create a vertical 9:16 TikTok ecommerce video. Use the uploaded product reference as the primary subject and keep the product appearance consistent. Maintain natural motion, realistic lighting, stable hands/objects, clean product focus, and a fast TikTok pacing. Avoid unrelated objects, broken anatomy, duplicated products, deformed packaging, unreadable text, flicker, and camera shake. User objective: 复刻这个视频的画面细节，包括画面构图、色彩、光影等：. Reference asset: image / 20260325180045_586_43.png. Reference frames extracted: 1. Reference source title: 复刻爆款 · https://www.tiktok.com/@auto.parts.store.tina/video/7619658308009528596. Ecommerce analysis summary: 正在生成脚本、分镜和提示词。. Storyboard: 镜头 1：画面 竖屏镜头，参考 3.1s - 8.3s 的原视频节奏。 当前任务目标：复刻这个视频的画面细节，包括画面构图、色彩、光影等：。；拍摄提示 围绕这段真实内容复刻画面与镜头推进：Hello, boss. How are you? I\'m Tina. Do you know I will be waiting for you.；旁白 Hello, boss. How are you? I\'m Tina. Do you know I will be waiting for you.；字幕 Hello, boss.；剪辑 保持 TikTok 的剪辑速度，参考 32.31fps 与 1080x1920，整条视频时长约 27.9 秒。。\n镜头 2：画面 竖屏镜头，参考 8.3s - 15.8s 的原视频节